WEBVTT

00:05.238 --> 00:08.807
<i>Those fingers in my head</i>

00:08.808 --> 00:12.678
<i>That sly, come-hither stare</i>

00:12.679 --> 00:15.514
<i>That strips my conscience bare</i>

00:15.515 --> 00:17.950
<i>It's witchcraft</i>

00:18.803 --> 00:21.220
- Salem, did I hear you singing?
- No, I was just...

00:21.221 --> 00:23.422
It's okay.
I came in 'cause it sounded good.

00:23.423 --> 00:26.025
Oh come on, enough. Ya think?

00:26.026 --> 00:28.293
Yeah. I just wanted a front row seat.

00:28.294 --> 00:30.496
- Me too.
- Right behind you.

00:30.497 --> 00:32.164
Well, well, well.
Ol' yellow eyes,

00:32.165 --> 00:33.399
you've still got it.

00:33.400 --> 00:34.433
Hit it cat.

00:34.634 --> 00:38.329
<i>And I've got
no defense for it</i>

00:38.338 --> 00:41.907
<i>The heat is too
intense for it</i>

00:42.208 --> 00:46.278
<i>What good would common sense
For it do...</i>

